CHESTER, CONCORD, CORNWELL, GASTONIA, GREAT FALLS, HUNTERSVILLE,
INDIAN TRAIL, KANNAPOLIS, MATTHEWS, MONROE, ROCK HILL, TRINITY,
AND WEDDINGTON.
